s of 2020 classmates for Virtual Grad Fest!  Virtual Grad Fest is an interactive experience exclusively for the Class of 2020. Learn about alumni benefits and resources while completing tasks and challenges for your chance to win prizes.  When: Monday, May 4 – Friday, May 10. Complete tasks on your own time throughout the week.  Where: Your smartphone or computer.  How:  1.) Download Scavify on your Android or iOS device and create a log in.  2.) Search for "UIC Virtual Grad Fest"  3.) Enter in the password "UICGrad20", and join the event.  If you do not have a smart phone, you may also participate by visiting https://app.scavify.com/#/ on your computer.  Contact the UIC Alumni Association at UICalumni@uic.edu with any questions.    Contact  Michelle Mittelman  312-996-2238  UICalumni@uic.edu     Date posted  Apr 28, 2020    Date updated  Apr 28, 2020                    UIC Logo        Engineering Career Center       Contact   851 S. Morgan St. | 800 SEO | Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-8374  rcconroy@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    LinkedIn    Twitter    Instagram            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 